room_title: Escape room "Locker Room Heist" by Twin Peaks Escape Room in Longmont
room_address: 425 South Bowen St. Unit #6 Longmont, CO 80501
room_description: Your team was in the championship but the other team cheated! They are at the pep rally celebrating their ill-gotten win. Now is your chance! You are going to get that trophy one way or another! You need to find a way into the coach’s ofﬁce and get back that trophy!
